ck\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xeu1665702671037.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xeu1665702671037.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xeu1665702671037.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xeu1665702671037\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file is the default initialization file for Uniface applications.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__section_w5777ab1b5b1_w5778ab1b5_w5779ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__table_d18689e1_d18690e1_d18691e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default location: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Depends on the value specified by the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eiq1665702549359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eiq1665702549359.html\" title=\"Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located.\">/adm</a> switch.<p class=\"p\">In Uniface installation, a\n                              <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file is located in\n                              <span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface/adm</span> and <span class=\"ph filepath\">/common/adm</span>\n</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__section_w5780ab1b5b3_w5781ab1b5_w5782ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d522725e96\">Unix </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__p_d177350e1_d177351e1_d177352e1\">On Unix, the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file contains only the [install] and [webwidgets] sections.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__section_w5783ab1b5b5_w5784ab1b5_w5785ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d522725e108\">File Sections </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54248e1_d54249e1_d54250e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fuu1665702671109.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fuu1665702671109.html\" title=\"The [accelerators] section of the initialization file enables you to map a logical function, such as fileopen to a keyboard sequence (an accelerator) such as Ctrl+F7.\">[accelerators]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54251e1_d54252e1_d54253e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54254e1_d54255e1_d54256e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lar1665702646046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lar1665702646046.html\" title=\"The [background] and [foreground] sections of the initialization file determine how Uniface video attributes are mapped to Uniface index colors for Windows and character mode applications.\">[background] and [foreground]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54257e1_d54258e1_d54259e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zfh1665702671886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfh1665702671886.html\" title=\"The [colorbox] section of the assignment file defines the Custom Colors palette of the Windows Color dialog box.\">[colorbox]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54260e1_d54261e1_d54262e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"crw1665702612934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crw1665702612934.html\" title=\"Use the [ENTITIES] section of the assignment file to direct individual entities to a path, give the target database table a different name than the name of the entity, or specify the physical file name for database tables for record-level databases.\">[ENTITIES]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54263e1_d54264e1_d54265e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rve1665702672162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rve1665702672162.html\" title=\"The [CHUI] section of the initialization file enables you to define the appearance of a character based application.\">[chui]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54266e1_d54267e1_d54268e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nvl1665702672374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvl1665702672374.html\" title=\"The [graphic filters] section of the initialization file specifies the graphic filter DLLs that allow Uniface to support particular image file formats.\">[graphic filters]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54269e1_d54270e1_d54271e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"igs1665702672514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/igs1665702672514.html\" title=\"The [help] section of the initialization file specifies the files to be used when online help is requested by the help ProcScript statement from a Uniface application, or within displayed messages.\">[help]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54272e1_d54273e1_d54274e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svo1665702672793.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svo1665702672793.html\" title=\"The [history] section records the most recent command lines used to start Uniface. A maximum of 10 command lines can be recorded.\">[history]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54275e1_d54276e1_d54277e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efz1665702672861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efz1665702672861.html\" title=\"The [install] section of the initialization file contains information about the current installation.\">[install]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54278e1_d54279e1_d54280e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zhw1665702673663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zhw1665702673663.html\" title=\"The [layout] section of the initialization file is used to specify whether and where form layout are stored.\">[layout]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54281e1_d54282e1_d54283e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exp1665702673803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exp1665702673803.html\" title=\"The [ocx] section of the initialization file is used to specify information about the environment in which OCXs run.\">[ocx]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54284e1_d54285e1_d54286e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gbz1665702543976.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gbz1665702543976.html\" title=\"Use the [PATHS] section of the assignment file to define paths to network and database connectors, which connect to a Uniface Server, DBMS, or to another path. Path assignments can include path-to-connector assignments and path-to-path assignments.\">[PATHS]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54287e1_d54288e1_d54289e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vas1665702670549.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vas1665702670549.html\" title=\"The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions.\">[printer]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54290e1_d54291e1_d54292e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ivc1665702674015.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ivc1665702674015.html\" title=\"The [procbox] section of the initialization file enables you to configure colors in the ProcScript Editor and HTML Source editor.\">[procbox]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54293e1_d54294e1_d54295e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xwv1665702674089.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xwv1665702674089.html\" title=\"This section of the initialization file records the state of certain UPI objects when the user exits an application.\">[state]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54296e1_d54297e1_d54298e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qjq1665702674162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qjq1665702674162.html\" title=\"The [toolbar] section of the initialization file controls the content of the Uniface toolbar, which is available for all Uniface client/server applications. All settings in this section are automatically updated by Uniface whenever it terminates.\">[toolbar]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54299e1_d54300e1_d54301e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"crc1665702674239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crc1665702674239.html\" title=\"The [udde] section controls the use of Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) support from within a Uniface application.\">[udde]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54302e1_d54303e1_d54304e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rpa1665702674458.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rpa1665702674458.html\" title=\"The [uniface_dlls] section of the initialization file specifies the DLLs used by Uniface.\">[uniface_dlls]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54305e1_d54306e1_d54307e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54308e1_d54309e1_d54310e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvv1665702674605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvv1665702674605.html\" title=\"The [user] section of the initialization file is optional. It contains the user name and optionally the password of the user who runs the current workstation.\">[user]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54311e1_d54312e1_d54313e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bdv1665702674820.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bdv1665702674820.html\" title=\"The [webwidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for fields used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.\">[webwidgets]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ouq1723639706136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ouq1723639706136.html\" title=\"The [webentitywidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for entities used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.\">[webentitywidgets]</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jub1770884848669.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jub1770884848669.html\" title=\"The [webcomponentwidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for components used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.\">[webcomponentwidgets]</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeu1665702671037__li_d54314e1_d54315e1_d54316e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tmu1665702674950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tmu1665702674950.html\" title=\"The [WIDGETS] section of the assignment file specifies logical to physical widget mappings for character mode. Default mappings are provided in the file usyschr.asn.\">[WIDGETS]</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exv1665702549479.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/ini</a><p>Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyp1665702675022.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Configuration Settings: Initialization</a><p>Initialization settings are used to configure the application on a specific platform.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "usys.ini Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The usys.ini file is the default initialization file for Uniface applications. Default location: Depends on the value specified by the /adm switch. In Uniface installation, a usys.ini file is located in /uniface/adm and /common/adm Unix On Unix, the usys.ini file contains only the [install] and [webwidgets] sections. File Sections [accelerators] [application] [background] and [foreground] [colorbox] [ENTITIES] [chui] [graphic filters] [help] [history] [install] [layout] [ocx] [PATHS] [printer] [procbox] [state] [toolbar] [udde] [uniface_dlls] [upi] [user] [webwidgets] [webentitywidgets] [webcomponentwidgets] [WIDGETS] Related Links /ini Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application. Configuration Settings: Initialization Initialization settings are used to configure the application on a specific platform. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}